formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
FOLLOWING THINGS ARE PROVIDED BY THE MANAGEMENT AND RELIED ON THE DATA
PROVIDED BY THE MANAGEMENT VIDE MANAGEMENT REPRESENTATION LETTER

1. As per the Management Representation Letter, in some of the flats payment has been received more than 10% of sale consideration but they have not done agreement for sale with the customers
2. As per the Management Representation Letter, some of the customers have insisted the firm to enter in sale deed and hence management have entered in sale deed and date of the same has been entered in Date of Agreement for sale. Hence they have not insisted for Agreement for Sale
3. Type of KYC, KYC ID and Mobile number are provided by Management and hence we certify based on Management Representation Letter. However we have verified the same based on test basis 
4. Actual Cost of Construction is not coherence as per Form 1 "Architect Certificate' and Form 2 "Engineer Certificate" due to non payment to the sundry creditors
5. Details of Project Loan / Lenders of Vardhman Green 1 BHK which is certified by the partner of Vardhman Realities is attached with Form 3 as Unsecured Loans
6. As per the Management Representation Letter, cost which is incurred and paid is greater than than the estimated cost did while applying for the RERA registration.
